com.amplifyframework.predictions

Class PredictionsCategory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.amplifyframework.core.category.Category<PredictionsPlugin<?>>
      • com.amplifyframework.predictions.PredictionsCategory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CategoryTypeable, PredictionsCategoryBehavior

    public final class PredictionsCategory
extends Category<PredictionsPlugin<?>>
implements PredictionsCategoryBehavior
    Defines the API that a consuming application uses to perform predictions. Internally routes calls to the registered plugins of the category.
